profile:
At Hilltop Interiors we offer personalized decorating to cater to your every need. Whether its a new home or an existing home that you are trying to freshen up, Hilltop Interiors is your one stop shop for your home or cottage needs.

All furniture and accessories can be delivered, installed, and assembled upon purchase. We deliver to Muskoka, Parry Sound, Collingwood, Orillia, Barrie, The Greater Toronto Area and anywhere in between. We ship anywhere in the World upon request.
service_area: Ontario Wide. Other locations can be negotiated.
